pure discrimination.

100
00:06:38,374 --> 00:06:39,707
(GIRLS BULLYING): Ha-ha-ha!

101
00:06:39,807 --> 00:06:42,640
Gymnastics is for
girls, [inaudible].

102
00:06:42,740 --> 00:06:44,607
Go find your own sport.

103
00:06:44,707 --> 00:06:46,040
Get outta here!

104
00:06:46,140 --> 00:06:48,940
-But now we've sworn to prove
that Martial Men's Gymnastics

105
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:53,640
is a manly sport, with manly
grace for manly men-like men.

106
00:06:53,740 --> 00:06:55,007
[sobbing]

107
00:06:55,107 --> 00:06:57,440
-You poor deluded fool.

108
00:06:57,540 --> 00:06:59,107
Real men don't wear tights.

109
00:06:59,207 --> 00:07:00,907
That's just for girls.

110
00:07:01,007 --> 00:07:04,474
