own in a fair fight?

117
00:07:19,774 --> 00:07:21,740
-If you call three to one fair.

118
00:07:39,607 --> 00:07:41,640
-So now are you convinced?

119
00:07:41,740 --> 00:07:42,740
Hand it over.

120
00:07:42,840 --> 00:07:44,940
-Akane, do something.

121
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:46,674
-If they get their
hands on this,

122
00:07:46,774 --> 00:07:49,640
Girl's Martial Arts
Gymnastics will be over.

123
00:07:49,740 --> 00:07:52,274
-Look, maybe you'd
better let me--

124
00:07:52,374 --> 00:07:56,974
-How far do we have to go
before you take us seriously?

125
00:07:57,074 --> 00:07:58,907
-How's this for serious?

126
00:07:59,007 --> 00:08:01,340
-Hmm?

127
00:08:01,440 --> 00:08:03,940
