joining Martial Men's Gymnastics

129
00:08:07,407 --> 00:08:08,674
after all.

130
00:08:08,774 --> 00:08:09,940
-Lucky me.

131
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:11,140
-Suit yourself.

132
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,774
Either way, we'll--

133
00:08:12,874 --> 00:08:14,107
-Perhaps this will.

134
00:08:16,974 --> 00:08:18,074
-Good thinking.

135
00:08:18,174 --> 00:08:21,140
