is in your hands.

150
00:08:55,707 --> 00:08:57,840
-But why does it have to?

151
00:08:57,940 --> 00:08:59,574
-Because you must, that's why.

152
00:08:59,674 --> 00:09:03,607
I Only you can combat the
menace of the boys in tights.

