156
00:09:07,974 --> 00:09:11,807
If you lose, you hand over the
final treasure without a fight.

157
00:09:11,907 --> 00:09:15,207
As a sign of good faith, we
will leave you to your training.

158
00:09:15,307 --> 00:09:15,748
Farewell.

159
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:27,840
-Look, Ranma.

160
00:09:27,940 --> 00:09:29,340
I don't want you to
take this the wrong way,

161
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:32,640
but I think it's probably better
if you let me handle this.

